嘅老師<br />\n<br />\n以第一個留言答覆為答案。大家可以俾d理性嘅意見我，等我可以改進個故事，多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"e484cb48299256a72ab5a6b3b0c05f1b614a4646","tid":937057,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc7910041e8baddb4b8ed148f95d026f49c9a6de","tid":937057,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"B"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"真係多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4740317d2af3e38eb37b847d78a53cfd80f8d971","tid":937057,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8747c6cf6e1915bba6ab132bedf8a9ac6275838d","tid":937057,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"228a071f69d800ed02d8400266342ef410499cb2","tid":937057,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe83e7cf153ec5a580770af401e7cd61b30820d1","tid":937057,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"ac9fdd93ef589af89bc8e3b4d8a19ce85ecf8523","tid":937057,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"係咪最後一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a17c50d6efabb956399f63e8aeb59ca49e58c17","tid":937057,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:34:40.000Z","msg":"阿俊心想: 搵佢屋企人應該好難，連登好似冇乜佢嘅資料，都係搵下當年任教過佢嘅老師。<br />\n<br />\n阿俊又找了一找，發現一篇有關事後校方回應的新聞 : <br />\n基魯書院副校長陳小麗表示校方將全力支援警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n「原來Miss chan當年係副校長? 點解佢依家變左英文科主任?」<br />\n阿俊知道Miss chan為人善良，對待學生更是十分親切，問她關於當年的事應該沒有問題。<br />\n<br />\n於是，第二天阿俊便去找Miss chan. <br />\n<br />\n「Miss chan...」<br />\n「嘩...俊仔大駕光臨，有何指教?」Miss chan笑道。<br />\n阿俊一時難為情，因為像他這樣的學生，幾乎不會主動找老師。<br />\n<br />\n「我想問下...你識唔識阿紅?」<br />\n「阿紅? 邊個阿紅呀? 惠英紅?哈哈..」Miss chan笑道。<br />\n「當年失蹤嘅女學生呀...」<br />\n此言一出，Miss chan立即收起笑容，一副正經的樣子說道 : <br />\n「點解你咁問? 校長講過唔準再講呢件事」<br />\n「你講俾我聽啦，我真係好想知」<br />\n阿俊不斷求她，於是Miss chan帶他到一個無人的課室，閉上門。<br />\n<br />\n阿俊心想 : 咁似...AV嘅劇情嘅..? 咁神秘做乜? <br />\nMiss chan : 「佢係我長年之前嘅學生，計返起上黎...已經有15年啦..」<br />\n「佢成績一向好好，當年佢嘅英文科成績仲特別優秀...真係可惜...」<br />\n阿俊說 : 「聽人講佢係俾人殺死，係咪真嫁?」<br />\nMiss chan現怒容 : 「亂講 ! 當年佢好乖，根本唔會得罪人，點會有人殺佢!?」<br />\n<br />\n忽然，只聽得一把聲 : 「Miss chan 點解你要同學生講呢d野?」<br />\n阿俊嚇了一跳 ，只見校長站在門口。<br />\n<br />\nMiss chan連忙說 : 「...時候唔早啦...同學你都係早d返屋企溫書啦!」<br />\n阿俊便立即離開，可是校長將他叫停，大聲說道 : 「以後再俾我聽到你講呢件事，我一定踢你出校! 」<br />\n<br />\n這時，阿俊會....<br />\n(A)屌返佢<br />\n(B)低下頭離開<br />\n(C)傻笑<br />\n<br />\n以第一個留言答覆為答案。大家可以俾d理性嘅意見我，等我可以改進個故事，多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"85cd51d4cbed18d2ca5efe50adeda88c8fa7066f","tid":937057,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac9fdd93ef589af89bc8e3b4d8a19ce85ecf8523","tid":937057,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"係咪最後一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:35:16.000Z","msg":"仲有，打埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正都冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f801e53ae334e0d5674e3d7e90213f0ae92eef","tid":937057,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"推~"},{"pid":"6b4ada430fa374627761757f3e1c4d936ef84c6e","tid":937057,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"3b819548368fe14d53fd89c58aff31d1eb33440f","tid":937057,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85cd51d4cbed18d2ca5efe50adeda88c8fa7066f","tid":937057,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid